reviewText: These are both very good movies, especially if you are a fan of Liam Neeson. I would recommend to anyone who likes an action packed movie.

If you like movies that have the exact same plot as the movie before, such as the Hangover and the Hangover 2, then you will like watching Taken (which is a good film) and then watching Taken 2 ( which has the same plot and less enthusiastic acting). Unless you just really like watching all of the actors that are involved in this film series; I would buy Taken and maybe rent Taken 2 for a dollar sometime, if you really need to watch it...
